Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬啟  曾我部學姐  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初夏過得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有件事想告訴學姐  於是就寫了這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  一副魂不守舍的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…今天早上開始就一直感覺到一股強烈的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小澪是名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是被誰監視著似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…別這樣看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是自我意識過剩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也能感覺到不知是從哪裡看著我的視線…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？感覺到誰的視線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我是一直都被別人狂看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小佐和就外表不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就」是什麼意思啊  「就」！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  尾行澪的犯人是小佐和？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  如果是我的話可不會只看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  犯人是小豬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想  小澪因為害怕小豬所以不太搭理它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是小豬就貼上小澪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  好可怕  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這幫人完全靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  大家都認真地為澪學姐擔心一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是被跟蹤狂盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  謎團全都解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…對不起  我只是想這樣做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我說謎團解開了是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  今天的早飯吃的是炒麵麵包吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  確…確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天早上睡過頭  就沒時間慢慢吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個炒麵麵包是打八折的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼連這個都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  這個東西黏在頭髮上了一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就被大家盯著了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在偷窺什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和  她們是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是什麼可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是澪學姐粉絲俱樂部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉絲俱樂部？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…我明明已經要忘記那件事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是來看小澪頭髮上黏標籤的樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  從別的會員那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是粉絲的話為什麼不立刻告訴她？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說告訴她比較好  但是…  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種東西黏在頭髮上才像是學姐  很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是故意黏上去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  都是因為我的關係  粉絲俱樂部的人才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但粉絲俱樂部還存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我還以為曾我部學姐畢業後就沒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部學姐是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  梓不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部學姐曾是小澪的粉絲俱樂部的會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  自那以後已經過了那麼長時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以後？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  那是在畢業典禮之前的3月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天澪也是覺得被別人盯著而感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不下去的我建議她去找學生會商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想也給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為誰都沒有認真地擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己去找學生會商量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一直被誰看著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟蹤狂什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難想像學校裡會有可疑人物…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能有這樣普通的反應讓我太高興了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社裡到底都是什麼反應啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真鍋同學  在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把交接的資料拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和  她是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是學生會長曾我部惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是「原」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照  秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然輕音社的人不認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是兩人的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之後等待著她們的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的澪還完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自加入奇怪的解說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼樣的命運？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用  雖然不如輕音社的茶好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  您太客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會有跟蹤狂  真是嚴重的問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真鍋同學  你等會兒能把這件事告訴風紀委員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  也不用這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我們學校的學生遇上了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想盡力幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓我們的社長聽一下這番話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但尾行澪的是什麼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是粉絲俱樂部之類的人…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒什麼  會長您對輕音社很瞭解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我的名字也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  連輕音社開茶會的事也知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是真鍋同學以前告訴我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我可沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是輕音社在各種意義上都很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  你掉了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山澪粉絲俱樂部會員證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛在走廊上撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是上面寫著學姐的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候我得說些什麼  把氣氛緩和下來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道會長就是犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說啥啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…其實會長就是尾行我的犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有惡意的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就要畢業了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到無法再見到秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就變得坐立不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被您這樣說我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然感到很害羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會員號1號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是粉絲俱樂部的會長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼學生會長就是犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在立場上這很難啟齒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們就考慮為這樣的曾我部學姐做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  於是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社讓我們到大禮堂來  會是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜什麼的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部學姐  恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐您畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們櫻高輕音社將帶著祝賀之意為您演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「軟軟呼呼Time」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…學姐  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未…未經允許就擅自使用大禮堂是不對的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那也只是原則上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次收到這種禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為紀念…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我簽個名！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請寫上「澪炭簽名」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰慧的學姐的形象…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了嗎…「澪炭」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會員號1號的會員證？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上面是和的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在那之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼真鍋同學  粉絲俱樂部的會長也一起交接給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·才·不·要·呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個會員證  我沒能拒絕就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:11:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果因為沒什麼機會  一直沒盡到做為會長的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天我是來拜託大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了粉絲俱樂部的會員  能開一場茶會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  這樣下去也對不起學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我們也會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直以來都受到和的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼決定了  那要開場什麼樣的茶會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連紬都…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你們冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…首先是隆重入場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有切蛋糕也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  送花和回憶相冊之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披露宴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話搞個提問環節怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒在聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}澪茶會時間表\N佈置澪商品（音樂室）\N澪入場（特別服務）\N紬的蛋糕（該怎麼辦呢？）\N蠟燭服務\N澪鼻眼鏡（爆笑表演？）\N提問環節\N來點幻燈片\N紀念品？\N照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶會的內容就交給大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就負責預定會場和聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做海報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶個特大的蛋糕來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  你投入過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  難得的華麗舞台～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家的幫助下  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以應該會成為很棒的茶會  曾我部學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺越來越像樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為小澪的粉絲準備的豪華盛宴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪鉛筆  小澪橡皮  小澪T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪巧克力  小澪開瓶器  小澪筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪搔癢耙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄出奇怪的東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是貼個小澪貼畫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然簡單但也挺可愛的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下這個會有人覺得高興嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂有烤餅乾哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪餅乾哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要說出「花了多少會費？」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？  講的別人好像守財奴一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  我們帶慰問品來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是炒麵麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連茶都備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…下手好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很期待茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎都很期待呢  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那最重要的曾我部學姐會過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  來不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然寫了信  但學姐說因為社團旅行所以趕不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒什麼意義了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要延後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐說既然通知出去了  就不必特意改日程了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部學姐只是希望粉絲俱樂部能夠繼續發展下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要茶會能讓現在的粉絲俱樂部成員覺得開心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好成熟的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女大學生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業成熟之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也從澪的粉絲中畢業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定只是碰巧撞上日程來不了而已啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  應該只是不想讓我們太操心罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我…如果我也畢業的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否也會成為那樣成熟的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時在澪的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同走馬燈般閃過一幕幕與朋友度過的美好時光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不要擅自加奇怪的解說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那日程就照計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切按原定進行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這是當天的流程表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司儀就拜託小律和小唯咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於會場的佈置方面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有什麼計劃  但我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂教室也不好整理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為大家做些什麼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓音樂教室顯得凌亂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從簡做起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在來確認一下流程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…真誠感謝大家參加第一次秋山澪粉絲俱樂部茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然冒昧  就請讓我們來擔任司儀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是田井中律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及平澤唯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:07.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎各位百忙中列坐到場…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  這是結婚典禮的司儀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:15.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…人生起起落落後…突然出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:16.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  那也是結婚典禮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多熟面孔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  佐佐木同學也是會員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短劇就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山澪粉絲俱樂部茶會現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請今天的主角登場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山～澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過穿制服好無聊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題！  還有宴會換裝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家今天在百忙中抽空集虧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬舌頭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也很…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集…集會到唱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板垣…退助？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我們的表演犀利多了  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼演講就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們開始切蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  有請小澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是初次的共同作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是提供蛋糕和茶點服務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及秋山澪本人的蠟燭服務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  這邊也要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們也該進入特別企劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是秋山澪百連問答！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  順帶一提  每回答一個問題就請熄滅桌上的一個蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始第一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止聽到過的最可怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你在問什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二可怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三可怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個下一個下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四可怕的事是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百物語？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你怕什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪同學～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼想問的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡的話先洗哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮…蓮蓬頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃鯛魚燒喜歡先吃頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃鰓蓋骨？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  讓我們進入下一個環節
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將用幻燈片來回顧小澪精彩的半輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17歲就已經半輩子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（秋山澪生活相冊）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…比起澪學姐  律學姐你是不是更搶鏡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我家相冊的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的茶會終於接近尾聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最後就由我們「放學後茶會」的演奏來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我有些東西想讓大家聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這張嘴比較笨拙講不好話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做了一首詩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  驚喜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ときめきシュガー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大切なあなたに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,カラメルソース
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,グラニュー糖に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ブラウンシュガー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,メープル　ハチミツ　和三盆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたのために　カラメルソース
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のハートも　カラメルソース
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっぴり焦げついちゃっても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火加減で　おいしくなるの！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人心跳的砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給重要的你塗滿糖汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細砂糖加上紅糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槭糖  蜂蜜  和三盆糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你塗滿糖汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也塗滿糖汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使稍微有點燒焦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會因你的火候而變得美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是粉絲也到達不了澪的境界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在開始演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放學後茶會」的新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「純潔之心」～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來來來來來來～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭の中　想いでいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あふれそうなの　ちょっと心配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:05.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,とりあえず　ヘッドホンで　ふさごう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲しいものは　欲しいって言うの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,したいことは　したいって言うの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:17.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど言えない言葉もあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stop the heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.11,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いきなり！　チャンス到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.15,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぐうぜん同じ帰り道　Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふくらむ胸の風船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急に足が宙に浮くの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上昇気流にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛んでいっちゃえ！　キミのもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたしの　ぴゅあぴゅあはーと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:47.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受けとめてくれるなら　恐くはないの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:53.27,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この気持ちが　大気圏　越えたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:56.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミは見えなくなってた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:02.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道の向こう側　あい★ Don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦海裡充滿了回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要溢出來了　有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:05.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先用耳機塞住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西就說想要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的東西就說想做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:17.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也有說不出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stop the heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.11,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間！ 機會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.15,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾走的是同一條回家的路　Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的氣球鼓了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然腳離開了地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著上升氣流而去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛走吧！ 飛到你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Pure Pure Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:47.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能接受的話　我就不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:53.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當這份心情穿越大氣圈的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:56.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:02.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道路的對面　I★ Don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  茄子～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後請向著這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都太挨著澪了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓曾我部學姐也看看這場景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照了又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發給曾我部學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  但是手機號碼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號碼就請學生會去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛の言葉ちりばめた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌は素直でいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.59,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにげに口ずさんで歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿菓子よりあまいメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.64,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火よりもあついリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:36.03,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きな曲は好きって言えるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stop my heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不意打ち!　ピンチ到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハミング　聞かれちゃったかも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:47.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!　はじめて　目があって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.21,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うれしいけど　はずかしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃げ腰なのよ　どうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突っ走っちゃえ!　道ばたで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふるえてる　ぴゅあぴゅあはーと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:05.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまでも透明な　あの空高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:08.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生まれたての…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}鑲嵌了愛的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}歌只要率真就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.59,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}無意間哼唱著前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Don't stop the music!
